the bank robbing career and life of America’s most wanted man was over.

00:21:03.585 --> 00:21:10.155
His successful capture by the FBI is thought to have been the one case that really catapulted

00:21:10.155 --> 00:21:16.885
the organisation to nationwide fame, to be an organisation that was deeply feared by criminals.

00:21:17.635 --> 00:21:23.365
Without Dillinger to lead it, the bank robbing gang was no more, and

00:21:23.525 --> 00:21:28.335
according to the FBI’s official website “The events of that sultry July

00:21:28.335 --> 00:21:33.205
night in Chicago marked the beginning of the end of the Gangster Era”.

