00:21:55.225 --> 00:22:00.195
Like all of the other characters we’ll encounter in this series, there’s no doubt that

00:22:00.475 --> 00:22:06.425
Dillinger was a criminal, a danger to society, and probably not a very nice man at all.

00:22:07.325 --> 00:22:13.645
