00:22:13.655 --> 00:22:18.975
Twins, who we will meet in the next episode, he seems a little bit less dangerous.

00:22:19.385 --> 00:22:23.325
Yes, he was a bankrobber, yes, he was probably also a

00:22:23.335 --> 00:22:27.495
